    dc:description "Fig. 9. Two other caligid genera from plankton samples. A, Lepeophtheirus semicossyphi Yamaguti, 1939, female (KMNH IvR 500,507), habitus, dorsal view; B, Metacaligus uruguayensis Thomsen, 1949, female (KMNH IvR 500,508), habitus, dorsal view.Scale bars: 1mm (A–B)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4649354/files/figure.png" ;
